						<p>c. 17th-18th Century.</p>						

						<p>This gives the names of several persons who contributed capital for the making of the image of the deity. The sculptor <hi rend="italic">(āchāri)</hi> was a Irāmaiyaṉ Chiṉṉakkoṇḍaṉ.</p>						

